    "Finally, LLMs have been used for the automatic evaluation of attribution.",
    "This involves determining the source or author of a piece of text.",
    "For example, an LLM could be used to determine whether a particular tweet was written by a specific person, or to identify the author of an anonymous piece of writing.",
